snippet.title: Path of Trials (0.1v)
snippet.description:
Join us on an exciting adventure in the game Path of Trials! In this video, you will see gameplay where the main character is a cute cat who will stop at nothing to save his owner. With each step, he faces new obstacles, but his determination knows no bounds. Immerse yourself in the world of Path of Trials and find out if our hero can overcome all the trials on his path! 
You can find the game on steam!
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2584480/Path_of_Trials/
